Terex Says China’s Platform Market Booms, Shanghai Daily Reports

-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 
2011-03-09T21:47:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-09/terex-says-china-s-platform-market-booms-shanghai-daily-reports.html
The market for aerial work
platforms in  China  is worth about $100 million to $150 million
and is expanding at 20 percent to 30 percent a year, Shanghai
Daily said today, citing X.S. Koo,  Terex Corp. (TEX) ’s managing
director for Asia-Pacific operations.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
